column1: # ProofKit Example: Powder Coat Cure with Data Gaps (Sensor Disconnection)
# Job: Decorative furniture coating batch PWC-2024-003
# Equipment: Dual PMT Sensor Array (TC-200 series)
# Description: Data gaps exceeding allowed threshold due to sensor disconnection during cure
# Expected Result: FAIL - data gaps too large for verification
# GAP: Sensor disconnection from 16:05:00 to 16:07:30 (2.5 minutes gap)
# GAP: Second sensor fails from 16:10:00 to 16:11:30
